<Author>touristsv
<Content>Got much more than my money's worth I am a returning customer to the hotel. I had arrived to Mexico City, this second time, to start postgraduate studies. I worried about my safety and cost. I can honestly say I got more than my moneys worth.Bus and subway stations are nearby. There are restaurants, where one I could dine cheaply and plentifully. My extra baggage was stored at no additional cost. I would leave my laptop at the receptionist's counter and they would send it to me quickly to my room if I needed so. Customer attention was admirable. I had reserved a room with fan, but some how it was given to someone else. I thought I would have to look for another place to stay, since no charge had been done to my credit card. All I carried was my email with the hotel's address. Nevertheless, they placed me at a higher rated room throughout my stay at no further cost.I have decided to return there as soon as I can. Just one thing, breakfast is not included and that is inconvenient if you are an early bird. 
