<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Excellent value Excellent value in its category. I stayed for a week in business and I enjoyed the hotel very much. Very clean, good size rooms, beautiful bathtroom and a very convenient location. Very helpful staff and the restaurant Wings good value and quality food and service. I would not hesitate to recommend it. I will use it as my hotel for future trips. I did have an executive single without A/C, but next time I will pay a little extra for the A/C, it is necessary for warm days and nights for us from the north. Not all rooms are air conditioned, although a big fan is provided. The electronic safe in the room very convenient, as is the mini bar, without the normally expensive prices. Enrique Schonfeldt 
